{"lang":"ko","stage":8,"title":"first sentences with linked ideas","sentences":[{"t":"원하면 있어도 돼요.","en":"You can stay if you want.","r":"wonhamyeon isseodo dwaeyo.","a":"n_1dac1ed6f8c4.mp3"},{"t":"이제 가야 해요.","en":"We have to leave now.","r":"ije gaya haeyo.","a":"n_eb0e4b2c9318.mp3"},{"t":"좀 도와줄 수 있어요?","en":"You could help me, please.","r":"jom dowajul su isseoyo?","a":"n_7298793d1a00.mp3"},{"t":"하고 싶은 대로 해요.","en":"Do whatever you want.","r":"hago sipeun daero haeyo.","a":"n_d5f7540f84f4.mp3"},{"t":"뭐든 물어봐요.","en":"Ask me whatever you want.","r":"mwodeun mureobwayo.","a":"n_51ff45f28dde.mp3"},{"t":"먼저 물어보고 나중에 얘기해요.","en":"Ask first, talk later.","r":"meonjeo mureobogo najunge yaegihaeyo.","a":"n_c67d19a431cc.mp3"},{"t":"그 사람 말이 맞다는 걸 보여 줬어요.","en":"He showed he was right.","r":"geu saram mari matdaneun geol boyeo jwosseoyo.","a":"n_5341a41b95f5.mp3"},{"t":"뭐든 시키고 싶은 거 시켜요.","en":"Order whatever you want.","r":"mwodeun sikigo sipeun geo sikyeoyo.","a":"n_39a233c7f3ca.mp3"},{"t":"먹어 봐요, 진짜 맛있어요.","en":"Try it, it's really tasty.","r":"meogeo bwayo, jinjja masisseoyo.","a":"n_5413351ee832.mp3"},{"t":"오늘 수요일인 것 같아요.","en":"It's Wednesday today, I think.","r":"oneul suyoirin geot gatayo.","a":"n_10297a27c921.mp3"},{"t":"길을 잃은 것 같아요.","en":"I think I'm lost.","r":"gireul ireun geot gatayo.","a":"n_b014e506523e.mp3"},{"t":"나갈 때 비가 오고 있었어요.","en":"It was raining when I went out.","r":"nagal ttae biga ogo isseosseoyo.","a":"n_21183b41fa52.mp3"},{"t":"오면 기다릴게요.","en":"If you come, I'll wait for you.","r":"omyeon gidarilgeyo.","a":"n_9b3d55828b80.mp3"},{"t":"도착하면 전화할게요.","en":"When I get there, I'll call you.","r":"dochakamyeon jeonhwahalgeyo.","a":"n_9d487d3a1042.mp3"},{"t":"아무것도 할 시간이 없어요.","en":"I don't have time for anything.","r":"amugeotdo hal sigani eopseoyo.","a":"n_220ecb62fa91.mp3"},{"t":"오늘은 아무것도 하기 싫어요.","en":"I don't want to do anything today.","r":"oneureun amugeotdo hagi sireoyo.","a":"n_516ff315dbde.mp3"},{"t":"오늘은 안 나가요.","en":"I'm not going out today.","r":"oneureun an nagayo.","a":"n_917c63c3e509.mp3"},{"t":"여기서는 그러지 않아요.","en":"We don't do that here.","r":"yeogiseoneun geureoji anayo.","a":"n_a896f4d1e416.mp3"},{"t":"시간이 조금 필요해요.","en":"I need a little time.","r":"sigani jogeum piryohaeyo.","a":"n_3c0df3df7f59.mp3"},{"t":"나중에 갈게요.","en":"I'm going to go later.","r":"najunge galgeyo.","a":"n_608a0978d690.mp3"},{"t":"먹을 거 좀 사야 해요.","en":"I need to buy something to eat.","r":"meogeul geo jom saya haeyo.","a":"n_d45f7e741658.mp3"},{"t":"아침에 스페인어 공부해요.","en":"I study Spanish in the morning.","r":"achime seupeineo gongbuhaeyo.","a":"n_10ebfb780d74.mp3"},{"t":"밥 할게요.","en":"I'm going to make the food.","r":"bap halgeyo.","a":"n_f5062fdd6122.mp3"},{"t":"오늘 먹을 거 사고 싶어요.","en":"I want to buy food for today.","r":"oneul meogeul geo sago sipeoyo.","a":"n_f85a04e839c4.mp3"},{"t":"여기 커피 얼마예요?","en":"How much is a coffee here?","r":"yeogi keopi eolmayeyo?","a":"n_b7caf1c41df5.mp3"},{"t":"매일 조금씩 공부해요.","en":"I study a little every day.","r":"maeil jogeumssik gongbuhaeyo.","a":"n_fcd7349104f9.mp3"},{"t":"추운 거 싫어요.","en":"I don't like the cold.","r":"chuun geo sireoyo.","a":"n_4dbc86d63c8e.mp3"},{"t":"다 같이 먹을 밥 했어요.","en":"I made food for everyone.","r":"da gachi meogeul bap haesseoyo.","a":"n_d8527fc24517.mp3"},{"t":"제 방은 항상 추워요.","en":"My room is always cold.","r":"je bangeun hangsang chuwoyo.","a":"n_bdc9180dab57.mp3"},{"t":"춥고 배고파요.","en":"I'm cold and I'm hungry.","r":"chupgo baegopayo.","a":"n_d544a814dc66.mp3"},{"t":"제 핸드폰 어디 있는지 알아요?","en":"Do you know where my phone is?","r":"je haendeupon eodi inneunji arayo?","a":"n_e18663b7ac2e.mp3"},{"t":"커피 시킬게요.","en":"I'm going to order a coffee.","r":"keopi sikilgeyo.","a":"n_071342303024.mp3"},{"t":"저는 아나 친구예요.","en":"I'm a friend of Ana's.","r":"jeoneun ana chinguyeyo.","a":"n_4cdc6a708cd2.mp3"},{"t":"이제 나갈 준비됐어요?","en":"Are you ready to go out yet?","r":"ije nagal junbidwaesseoyo?","a":"n_7b9b85df3bab.mp3"},{"t":"오늘 밤에 나갈래요?","en":"Would you like to go out tonight?","r":"oneul bame nagallaeyo?","a":"n_a65ae9b68d6e.mp3"},{"t":"뭐 좀 먹고 싶어요.","en":"I feel like eating something.","r":"mwo jom meokgo sipeoyo.","a":"n_9d22afb13ee0.mp3"},{"t":"나가기 전에 뭐 좀 먹는 게 좋아요.","en":"You should eat before you go out.","r":"nagagi jeone mwo jom meongneun ge joayo.","a":"n_049bbaa34689.mp3"},{"t":"저 왜 이러는지 모르겠어요.","en":"I don't know what's wrong with me.","r":"jeo wae ireoneunji moreugesseoyo.","a":"n_7a5fa570e41b.mp3"},{"t":"여기 아는 사람이 없어요.","en":"I don't know anyone here.","r":"yeogi aneun sarami eopseoyo.","a":"n_99980152bb0d.mp3"},{"t":"저는 항상 다 늦어요.","en":"I'm always late to everything.","r":"jeoneun hangsang da neujeoyo.","a":"n_234de16237d2.mp3"},{"t":"침대 정리 한 번도 안 해요.","en":"I never make the bed.","r":"chimdae jeongni han beondo an haeyo.","a":"n_84950e64d4f9.mp3"},{"t":"아침부터 아파요.","en":"It's hurt since this morning.","r":"achimbuteo apayo.","a":"n_d555c0523776.mp3"},{"t":"밤에 자러 가요.","en":"At night I go to bed.","r":"bame jareo gayo.","a":"n_4000e215b1cf.mp3"},{"t":"이 버스 시내로 가요?","en":"Does this bus go downtown?","r":"i beoseu sinaero gayo?","a":"n_c0420a0f77b6.mp3"},{"t":"그 사람 항상 똑같은 말 해요.","en":"He always says the same thing.","r":"geu saram hangsang ttokgateun mal haeyo.","a":"n_f6c2eb4dce25.mp3"},{"t":"그 이상은 말 못 해요.","en":"I can't tell you more than that.","r":"geu isangeun mal mot haeyo.","a":"n_1b8d4067ec2e.mp3"},{"t":"그 사람 집에서 운동해요.","en":"He works out at home.","r":"geu saram jibeseo undonghaeyo.","a":"n_35f55eecf7ef.mp3"},{"t":"식탁에 음식 있어요.","en":"There's food on the table.","r":"siktage eumsik isseoyo.","a":"n_74aa1862fde4.mp3"},{"t":"이번엔 좀 내 줄 수 있어요?","en":"Can you pay this time?","r":"ibeonen jom nae jul su isseoyo?","a":"n_62dd35d8a873.mp3"},{"t":"그 사람 이름이 뭔지 몰라요.","en":"I don't know what his name is.","r":"geu saram ireumi mwonji mollayo.","a":"n_8892627e7ee4.mp3"},{"t":"친구 이름이 뭐예요?","en":"What's your friend's name?","r":"chingu ireumi mwoyeyo?","a":"n_7147e49af2c4.mp3"},{"t":"제 친구 이름은 카를로스예요.","en":"My friend's name is Carlos.","r":"je chingu ireumeun kareulloseuyeyo.","a":"n_eaf9309f299c.mp3"},{"t":"주말이 더 나아요.","en":"The weekend works better.","r":"jumari deo naayo.","a":"n_6044c868b20f.mp3"},{"t":"잠깐 있다가 할게요.","en":"I'll do it in a moment.","r":"jamkkan itdaga halgeyo.","a":"n_28696305d0fc.mp3"},{"t":"좀 전까지 여기 있었어요.","en":"He was here a moment ago.","r":"jom jeonkkaji yeogi isseosseoyo.","a":"n_45a157a42a42.mp3"},{"t":"잠깐 얘기 좀 해요.","en":"I need to talk to you for a sec.","r":"jamkkan yaegi jom haeyo.","a":"n_24fa43d0a478.mp3"},{"t":"월요일엔 항상 졸려요.","en":"I'm always sleepy on Mondays.","r":"woryoiren hangsang jollyeoyo.","a":"n_2f05f7e66190.mp3"},{"t":"그거 사려면 돈이 필요해요.","en":"You need money to buy that.","r":"geugeo saryeomyeon doni piryohaeyo.","a":"n_3199ba910055.mp3"},{"t":"파티 할 거예요.","en":"We're going to throw a party.","r":"pati hal geoyeyo.","a":"n_994585694cff.mp3"},{"t":"월요일부터 아파요.","en":"I've been sick since Monday.","r":"woryoilbuteo apayo.","a":"n_12f5eaefc7d6.mp3"},{"t":"우리 형은 항상 배고파해요.","en":"My brother is always hungry.","r":"uri hyeongeun hangsang baegopahaeyo.","a":"n_1b9260e0bfae.mp3"},{"t":"매일 운동해요.","en":"I work out every day.","r":"maeil undonghaeyo.","a":"n_dc4d6aa48165.mp3"},{"t":"이거 좋아해요?","en":"Do you like this?","r":"igeo joahaeyo?","a":"n_b14016ba8b28.mp3"},{"t":"오늘은 맛있는 거 먹고 싶어요.","en":"Today I want to eat something tasty.","r":"oneureun masinneun geo meokgo sipeoyo.","a":"n_d1f6c9c88604.mp3"},{"t":"올 거예요, 안 올 거예요?","en":"Are you going to come or not?","r":"ol geoyeyo, an ol geoyeyo?","a":"n_02c1f8c50354.mp3"},{"t":"오늘 집에 늦게 와요.","en":"I'm coming home late today.","r":"oneul jibe neutge wayo.","a":"n_00b3a012f287.mp3"},{"t":"화장실에 누구 있어요?","en":"Who's in the bathroom?","r":"hwajangsire nugu isseoyo?","a":"n_504d5a830ddd.mp3"},{"t":"항상 화장실에 있네요.","en":"You're always in the bathroom.","r":"hangsang hwajangsire inneyo.","a":"n_120ead74e7cd.mp3"},{"t":"커피 마시러 가요.","en":"Let's go have a coffee.","r":"keopi masireo gayo.","a":"n_8bb94081bcde.mp3"},{"t":"제 방은 진짜 작아요.","en":"My room is really small.","r":"je bangeun jinjja jagayo.","a":"n_52138698f86b.mp3"},{"t":"시간이 진짜 빨리 가요.","en":"Time goes by really fast.","r":"sigani jinjja ppalli gayo.","a":"n_70592a24a42a.mp3"},{"t":"오늘 날씨 진짜 좋아요.","en":"The weather is really nice today.","r":"oneul nalssi jinjja joayo.","a":"n_52d196b0e5b4.mp3"},{"t":"우리 집 어떻게 오는지 알아요?","en":"Do you know how to get to my place?","r":"uri jip eotteoke oneunji arayo?","a":"n_ea67dc288fc7.mp3"},{"t":"누가 물어봤어요?","en":"Who asked you?","r":"nuga mureobwasseoyo?","a":"n_318f70751121.mp3"},{"t":"어디 사는지 물어봤어요.","en":"He asked me where I live.","r":"eodi saneunji mureobwasseoyo.","a":"n_07330d8227a0.mp3"},{"t":"그 사람 방에 있어요.","en":"She's in her room.","r":"geu saram bange isseoyo.","a":"n_084a696bb503.mp3"},{"t":"아침에 샤워해요.","en":"In the morning I shower.","r":"achime syawohaeyo.","a":"n_708041e4b92e.mp3"},{"t":"왜 그렇게 기분 좋아요?","en":"Why are you so happy?","r":"wae geureoke gibun joayo?","a":"n_6bea6074d930.mp3"},{"t":"우리 엄마 오늘 피곤해해요.","en":"My mom is tired today.","r":"uri eomma oneul pigonhaehaeyo.","a":"n_884be5218379.mp3"},{"t":"저는 운동 안 해요.","en":"I don't do any sports.","r":"jeoneun undong an haeyo.","a":"n_f25c7afff956.mp3"},{"t":"뭐 다른 거 사러 가요.","en":"I'm going to buy something else.","r":"mwo dareun geo sareo gayo.","a":"n_b70519f6919c.mp3"},{"t":"오늘 좋은 일 하나 했어요.","en":"I did one good thing today.","r":"oneul joeun il hana haesseoyo.","a":"n_65ea816314f5.mp3"},{"t":"그 사람 밤에 공부해요.","en":"He studies at night.","r":"geu saram bame gongbuhaeyo.","a":"n_56230def574f.mp3"},{"t":"다섯 시 십오 분이에요.","en":"It's a quarter past five.","r":"daseot si sibo bunieyo.","a":"n_19135f10528d.mp3"},{"t":"저한텐 너무 비싸요.","en":"That's too expensive for me.","r":"jeohanten neomu bissayo.","a":"n_4a2a087fbaa6.mp3"},{"t":"시험이 금요일이에요.","en":"The exam is on Friday.","r":"siheomi geumyoiri-eyo.","a":"n_dff47c5f092a.mp3"},{"t":"시험 때문에 긴장돼요.","en":"I'm nervous about the test.","r":"siheom ttaemune ginjangdwaeyo.","a":"n_89a6ab3d8935.mp3"},{"t":"시험 볼 준비됐어요.","en":"We're ready for the test.","r":"siheom bol junbidwaesseoyo.","a":"n_bbf388bf82d8.mp3"},{"t":"강아지가 몇 살이에요?","en":"How old is your dog?","r":"gangajiga myeot sari-eyo?","a":"n_bd8478898ed9.mp3"},{"t":"제 동생은 열 살이에요.","en":"My sister is ten years old.","r":"je dongsaengeun yeol sari-eyo.","a":"n_9588fd794fff.mp3"},{"t":"집에 있는 거 좋아해요.","en":"I like being at home.","r":"jibe inneun geo joahaeyo.","a":"n_1402a66f5ba0.mp3"},{"t":"잠깐 나갔다 올게요.","en":"I'm going to go out for a bit.","r":"jamkkan nagatda olgeyo.","a":"n_b94bb364fcf8.mp3"},{"t":"조금 더 있고 싶어요.","en":"I want to stay a little longer.","r":"jogeum deo itgo sipeoyo.","a":"n_a039f400ae77.mp3"},{"t":"어디 있는지 누구한테 물어봐요.","en":"Ask someone where it is.","r":"eodi inneunji nuguhante mureobwayo.","a":"n_2213240230eb.mp3"}]}